      "cookedHtml": "<p>When I click on a task on the default table view I can see a summary of updates however if I look on  different view within the same board I can see the task updates on the right hand side but I can also see the task info / columns info on the left hand side. Could you make this consistent so that we can see the task info as well as the task updates when we click on the task please?<br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/8/a/8a6e987c79e4584a85132637d106ea2b351f7c3e.jpeg\" title=\"Main table task view\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/8/a/8a6e987c79e4584a85132637d106ea2b351f7c3e_2_690x354.jpeg\" alt=\"Main table task view\" width=\"690\" height=\"354\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">Main table task view</span><span class=\"informations\">1908×980 190 KB</span></div></a></div><br />\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/6/b/6bb1ed9f6b46aafb1433af444e5543c73ef795dd.jpeg\" title=\"secondary board\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/6/b/6bb1ed9f6b46aafb1433af444e5543c73ef795dd_2_690x475.jpeg\" alt=\"secondary board\" width=\"690\" height=\"475\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">secondary board</span><span class=\"informations\">1449×998 146 KB</span></div></a></div><br />\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/2/b/2b044ea2dce7e33f9f67ef0116d59d48c3877fc5.jpeg\" title=\"secondary table task view\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/2/b/2b044ea2dce7e33f9f67ef0116d59d48c3877fc5_2_690x358.jpeg\" alt=\"secondary table task view\" width=\"690\" height=\"358\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">secondary